<item>
            <title>[JCRVLT-359] Provide separate option to control handling of rep:cugPolicy nodes.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/JCRVLT-359</link>
                <project id="12314920" key="JCRVLT">Jackrabbit FileVault</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently handling of rep:cugPolicy nodes is controlled by aclHandling configuration option that equally affects ACLs and CUGs. We need to control them separately as for replication that is based on sling-distribution we need to ignore ACLs while overwriting CUGs&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
